{"tid":981329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢不滿要自助點餐 老麥內發爛渣搗亂","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T08:21:33.000Z","uid":166622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88a57131de5571c7ebe3f8ecc40afc68461d6f99","tid":981329,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:21:33.000Z","msg":"中環皇后大道中號一間麥當勞快餐店，今日（14日）凌晨2時許，一名南亞漢進入光顧時，因不滿需到自助點餐機購買食物，有感被待慢，大為不滿，登時「發爛渣」，在店內肆意搗亂，推倒水吧內的玻璃杯及瓷碟，並踢毀一度木門，然後悻然離去，職員報警求助。警員到場調查，列為刑事毀壞案，正追緝涉案南亞漢歸案，他身高約1.7米，案發時身穿白、綠色上衣及卡其色長褲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jgnfeK.WVlVQQRf_JDvApQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/6323596e9d57ba128acfaaf108495b01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjgnfeK.WVlVQQRf_JDvApQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTg1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F6323596e9d57ba128acfaaf108495b01&h=f026139e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}